{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "title": "CI/CD Pipeline Health Dashboard",
    "tags": ["ci-cd", "pipeline", "freightliner"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "refresh": "30s",
    "time": {
      "from": "now-6h",
      "to": "now"
    },
    "timepicker": {
      "refresh_intervals": ["30s", "1m", "5m", "15m", "30m", "1h", "2h", "1d"]
    },
    "templating": {
      "list": [
        {
          "name": "api_host",
          "type": "custom",
          "label": "API Host",
          "query": "localhost,127.0.0.1,0.0.0.0",
          "current": {
            "text": "localhost",
            "value": "localhost"
          },
          "options": [
            {"text": "localhost", "value": "localhost", "selected": true},
            {"text": "127.0.0.1", "value": "127.0.0.1"},
            {"text": "0.0.0.0", "value": "0.0.0.0"}
          ],
          "includeAll": false,
          "multi": false,
          "skipUrlSync": false,
          "hide": 0
        },
        {
          "name": "api_port",
          "type": "custom",
          "label": "API Port",
          "query": "8080,9090,3000,8888",
          "current": {
            "text": "8080",
            "value": "8080"
          },
          "options": [
            {"text": "8080", "value": "8080", "selected": true},
            {"text": "9090", "value": "9090"},
            {"text": "3000", "value": "3000"},
            {"text": "8888", "value": "8888"}
          ],
          "includeAll": false,
          "multi": false,
          "skipUrlSync": false,
          "hide": 0
        },
        {
          "name": "deployment_mode",
          "type": "custom",
          "label": "Deployment Mode",
          "query": "local,remote,cloud",
          "current": {
            "text": "local",
            "value": "local"
          },
          "options": [
            {"text": "local", "value": "local", "selected": true},
            {"text": "remote", "value": "remote"},
            {"text": "cloud", "value": "cloud"}
          ],
          "includeAll": false,
          "multi": false,
          "skipUrlSync": false,
          "hide": 0
        },
        {
          "name": "workflow",
          "type": "query",
          "label": "Workflow",
          "query": "label_values(github_actions_workflow_runs_total, workflow_name)",
          "refresh": "on_time_range_change",
          "includeAll": true,
          "allValue": ".*",
          "datasource": "prometheus"
        },
        {
          "name": "scenario",
          "type": "query",
          "label": "Load Test Scenario",
          "query": "label_values(load_test_throughput_mbps, scenario)",
          "refresh": "on_time_range_change",
          "includeAll": true,
          "allValue": ".*",
          "datasource": "prometheus"
        },
        {
          "name": "instance",
          "type": "query",
          "label": "Instance",
          "query": "label_values(node_cpu_seconds_total, instance)",
          "refresh": "on_time_range_change",
          "includeAll": true,
          "allValue": ".*",
          "datasource": "prometheus"
        }
      ]
    },
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "API Connection Status",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 0},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "up{job=\"api_metrics\"}",
            "legendFormat": "API Status",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [
              {"type": "value", "options": {"0": {"text": "DOWN", "color": "red"}}},
              {"type": "value", "options": {"1": {"text": "UP", "color": "green"}}}
            ],
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"color": "red", "value": 0},
                {"color": "green", "value": 1}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "none",
          "justifyMode": "center",
          "text": {
            "titleSize": 16,
            "valueSize": 40
          }
        },
        "pluginVersion": "9.0.0"
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "API Endpoint Configuration",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 0},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "**API Endpoint Configuration**\n\nðŸ“ **Endpoint URL**: `http://$api_host:$api_port/metrics`\n\nðŸŒ **Deployment Mode**: `$deployment_mode`\n\nâš™ï¸ **Status**: Connected\n\n---\n\n**Quick Actions:**\n- Change host/port using dropdowns above\n- Switch deployment mode for different configs\n- All panels update automatically"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Deployment Mode Info",
        "type": "text",
        "gridPos": {"h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 0},
        "options": {
          "mode": "markdown",
          "content": "**Deployment Modes**\n\nðŸ  **Local**: Development environment (localhost)\n- Default: localhost:8080\n- No authentication required\n\nâ˜ï¸ **Remote**: Staging/Testing servers\n- Custom hostname/IP\n- Basic authentication\n\nðŸŒ **Cloud**: Production environment\n- Cloud provider endpoints\n- Full authentication + TLS"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 10,
        "title": "Pipeline Success Rate",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 6},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(github_actions_workflow_runs_total{conclusion=\"success\"}[1h]) / rate(github_actions_workflow_runs_total[1h]) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Success Rate"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "percent",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"color": "red", "value": 0},
                {"color": "yellow", "value": 90},
                {"color": "green", "value": 95}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "area",
          "justifyMode": "center",
          "orientation": "horizontal"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 11,
        "title": "Average Build Duration",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 6},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(github_actions_workflow_duration_seconds) / 60",
            "legendFormat": "Avg Duration"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "minutes",
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"color": "green", "value": 0},
                {"color": "yellow", "value": 5},
                {"color": "red", "value": 10}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "area",
          "justifyMode": "center"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 12,
        "title": "Load Test Throughput",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 6},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg(load_test_throughput_mbps)",
            "legendFormat": "Throughput"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "MBs",
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"color": "red", "value": 0},
                {"color": "yellow", "value": 25},
                {"color": "green", "value": 50}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background",
          "graphMode": "area",
          "justifyMode": "center"
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 13,
        "title": "Security Vulnerabilities",
        "type": "stat",
        "gridPos": {"h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 6},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(security_vulnerabilities_total{severity=\"critical\"})",
            "legendFormat": "Critical"
          },
          {
            "expr": "sum(security_vulnerabilities_total{severity=\"high\"})",
            "legendFormat": "High"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "unit": "short",
            "thresholds": {
              "steps": [
                {"color": "green", "value": 0},
                {"color": "yellow", "value": 1},
                {"color": "red", "value": 5}
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        "options": {
          "colorMode": "background",
          "reduceOptions": {
            "values": false,
            "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
          }
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 14,
        "title": "Pipeline Build Success Rate Over Time",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "rate(github_actions_workflow_runs_total{conclusion=\"success\"}[5m]) / rate(github_actions_workflow_runs_total[5m]) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Success Rate"
          },
          {
            "expr": "rate(github_actions_workflow_runs_total{conclusion=\"failure\"}[5m]) / rate(github_actions_workflow_runs_total[5m]) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Failure Rate"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "label": "Percentage",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "unit": "percent"
          }
        ],
        "legend": {
          "show": true,
          "values": true,
          "current": true,
          "avg": true
        },
        "thresholds": [
          {
            "value": 95,
            "colorMode": "critical",
            "op": "lt",
            "fill": true,
            "line": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 15,
        "title": "Build Duration Distribution",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, github_actions_workflow_duration_seconds_bucket) / 60",
            "legendFormat": "P50"
          },
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, github_actions_workflow_duration_seconds_bucket) / 60",
            "legendFormat": "P95"
          },
          {
            "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, github_actions_workflow_duration_seconds_bucket) / 60",
            "legendFormat": "P99"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "label": "Duration",
            "unit": "minutes"
          }
        ],
        "legend": {
          "show": true,
          "values": true,
          "current": true
        },
        "thresholds": [
          {
            "value": 10,
            "colorMode": "critical",
            "op": "gt",
            "fill": true,
            "line": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 16,
        "title": "Load Test Performance Metrics",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 23},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "load_test_throughput_mbps",
            "legendFormat": "Throughput (MB/s) - {{scenario}}"
          },
          {
            "expr": "load_test_p99_latency_ms / 1000",
            "legendFormat": "P99 Latency (s) - {{scenario}}"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "label": "Throughput (MB/s) / Latency (s)",
            "min": 0
          }
        ],
        "legend": {
          "show": true,
          "values": true,
          "current": true,
          "avg": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 17,
        "title": "Memory Usage During Load Tests",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 23},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "load_test_memory_usage_mb",
            "legendFormat": "Memory Usage (MB) - {{scenario}}"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "label": "Memory (MB)",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 4096
          }
        ],
        "legend": {
          "show": true,
          "values": true,
          "current": true,
          "max": true
        },
        "thresholds": [
          {
            "value": 2048,
            "colorMode": "critical",
            "op": "gt",
            "fill": true,
            "line": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 18,
        "title": "Docker Build Performance",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 32},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "docker_build_duration_seconds{stage=\"builder\"} / 60",
            "legendFormat": "Builder Stage"
          },
          {
            "expr": "docker_build_duration_seconds{stage=\"test\"} / 60",
            "legendFormat": "Test Stage"
          },
          {
            "expr": "docker_build_duration_seconds{stage=\"build\"} / 60",
            "legendFormat": "Build Stage"
          },
          {
            "expr": "docker_build_duration_seconds{stage=\"final\"} / 60",
            "legendFormat": "Final Stage"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "label": "Duration (minutes)",
            "min": 0
          }
        ],
        "legend": {
          "show": true,
          "values": true,
          "current": true,
          "avg": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 19,
        "title": "Security Scan Results",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 32},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "security_vulnerabilities_total{severity=\"critical\"}",
            "legendFormat": "Critical"
          },
          {
            "expr": "security_vulnerabilities_total{severity=\"high\"}",
            "legendFormat": "High"
          },
          {
            "expr": "security_vulnerabilities_total{severity=\"medium\"}",
            "legendFormat": "Medium"
          },
          {
            "expr": "security_vulnerabilities_total{severity=\"low\"}",
            "legendFormat": "Low"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "label": "Count",
            "min": 0
          }
        ],
        "legend": {
          "show": true,
          "values": true,
          "current": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 20,
        "title": "Test Execution Metrics",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 41},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "test_execution_duration_seconds / 60",
            "legendFormat": "Test Duration (min) - {{suite_name}}"
          },
          {
            "expr": "test_coverage_percent",
            "legendFormat": "Coverage % - {{package}}"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "label": "Duration (min) / Coverage (%)",
            "min": 0
          }
        ],
        "legend": {
          "show": true,
          "values": true,
          "current": true,
          "avg": true
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 21,
        "title": "Resource Utilization",
        "type": "graph",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 41},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "100 - (avg by (instance) (irate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode=\"idle\"}[5m])) * 100)",
            "legendFormat": "CPU Usage % - {{instance}}"
          },
          {
            "expr": "(node_memory_MemTotal_bytes - node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes) / node_memory_MemTotal_bytes * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Memory Usage % - {{instance}}"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "label": "Percentage",
            "min": 0,
            "max": 100,
            "unit": "percent"
          }
        ],
        "legend": {
          "show": true,
          "values": true,
          "current": true,
          "avg": true
        },
        "thresholds": [
          {
            "value": 80,
            "colorMode": "critical",
            "op": "gt",
            "fill": true,
            "line": true
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": 22,
        "title": "Pipeline SLA Compliance",
        "type": "table",
        "gridPos": {"h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 50},
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "avg_over_time(github_actions_workflow_duration_seconds[24h]) / 60",
            "legendFormat": "Avg Build Time (24h)",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          },
          {
            "expr": "(rate(github_actions_workflow_runs_total{conclusion=\"success\"}[24h]) / rate(github_actions_workflow_runs_total[24h])) * 100",
            "legendFormat": "Success Rate (24h)",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          },
          {
            "expr": "avg_over_time(load_test_throughput_mbps[24h])",
            "legendFormat": "Avg Throughput (24h)",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          },
          {
            "expr": "sum(security_vulnerabilities_total{severity=\"critical\"})",
            "legendFormat": "Critical Vulns",
            "format": "table",
            "instant": true
          }
        ],
        "transformations": [
          {
            "id": "merge",
            "options": {}
          },
          {
            "id": "organize",
            "options": {
              "excludeByName": {"Time": true},
              "renameByName": {
                "Value #A": "Build Time (min)",
                "Value #B": "Success Rate (%)",
                "Value #C": "Throughput (MB/s)",
                "Value #D": "Critical Vulns"
              }
            }
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "overrides": [
            {
              "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Build Time (min)"},
              "properties": [
                {
                  "id": "thresholds",
                  "value": {
                    "steps": [
                      {"color": "green", "value": 0},
                      {"color": "yellow", "value": 5},
                      {"color": "red", "value": 10}
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                  "value": {"type": "color-background"}
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Success Rate (%)"},
              "properties": [
                {
                  "id": "thresholds",
                  "value": {
                    "steps": [
                      {"color": "red", "value": 0},
                      {"color": "yellow", "value": 90},
                      {"color": "green", "value": 95}
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                  "value": {"type": "color-background"}
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "matcher": {"id": "byName", "options": "Critical Vulns"},
              "properties": [
                {
                  "id": "thresholds",
                  "value": {
                    "steps": [
                      {"color": "green", "value": 0},
                      {"color": "red", "value": 1}
                    ]
                  }
                },
                {
                  "id": "custom.cellOptions",
                  "value": {"type": "color-background"}
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ],
    "annotations": {
      "list": [
        {
          "name": "Deployments",
          "datasource": "prometheus",
          "expr": "increase(github_actions_workflow_runs_total{conclusion=\"success\", workflow_name=\"release\"}[1m])",
          "textFormat": "Deployment completed (Mode: $deployment_mode)",
          "tags": ["deployment"],
          "iconColor": "green"
        },
        {
          "name": "Critical Alerts",
          "datasource": "prometheus",
          "expr": "ALERTS{alertstate=\"firing\", severity=\"critical\"}",
          "textFormat": "{{alertname}}: {{summary}} (API: $api_host:$api_port)",
          "tags": ["alert", "critical"],
          "iconColor": "red"
        },
        {
          "name": "API Connection Events",
          "datasource": "prometheus",
          "expr": "changes(up{job=\"api_metrics\"}[1m]) > 0",
          "textFormat": "API connection status changed (http://$api_host:$api_port/metrics)",
          "tags": ["api", "connection"],
          "iconColor": "blue"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
